item.title: To play a server with hamachi do you need to have hamachi?
item.dc:creator: @Javacisnotrecognized _^_
item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

Hamachi is; in short; a peer - to - peer networking device. I personally never have used the thing, because I have more brain cells than a common goldfish and do not require it. If a server is marked [Ham], then the person who’s running it was a lazy bastard and fell back on Hamachi.

If you wan’t to go on a server that is run by someone who uses Hamachi, you also require Hamachi.
